title: The Power of Community Medicine
itunes:title: The Power of Community Medicine
description: This episode features Dr. James Allen, the founder and CEO of Health Systems Thinkers. Dr. Allen went from being a small-town physician in upstate New York, to working for a company in Borneo and later Bangladesh.  In the process, he became one of the foremost authorities on community medicine. Being in a remote small town made him see the workplace as part of the community.
author: CVS Health
